Summary of fixes:
1. LOCF excludes baseline from carry-forward pool (locf_baseline)
2. AWHI for Week 24 = 336 (awhi_week24)
3. AWLO for Week 8 = 29 (awlo_week8)
4. Visit windowing uses AWLO/AWHI range check (visit_window_range)
